{"tid":2455120,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Flightsim撚]模擬飛行集中討論區(31)","createTime":"2021-03-20T20:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T05:42:35.000Z","uid":56206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d83036357bd72353e688e32492f2e7077443d72","tid":2455120,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.prepar3d.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Water-w-logo-1-900x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prepar3d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FWater-w-logo-1-900x400.jpg&h=da02a791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPrepar3D（發音為&quot;prepared&quot;）為Lockheed Martin基於FSX開發，是一個結合真實與訓練的模擬平台，容許用戶在航空,海事和地面領域創建訓練場景，進行身臨其境的體驗式學習。<br />\n用戶可以在虛擬世界的任何地方進行訓練，包括水底和近地軌道空間。<br />\nPrepar3D同時保持與FSX的兼容性，用戶在Prepar3D中使用數千個附加組件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-cf.gamivo.com/image_original.jpg?f=56852&amp;n=6644132406370855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-cf.gamivo.com%2Fimage_original.jpg%3Ff%3D56852%26n%3D6644132406370855.jpg&h=83f7501a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nX-plane系列第十一代作品,提供更逼真的體驗，支援Mac OS X，Windows，Linux操作系統。<br />\n全新的&ldquo;Physically Based Rendering&rdquo;渲染引擎使照明和反射以物理正確的方式表現，並根據視角和物體的表面而改變。<br />\n這種技術使圖形效果不再需要預先渲染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1250410/header.jpg?t=1597159746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1250410%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1597159746&h=84698650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMicrosoft Flight Simulator使用Bing Maps的紋理和地形數據模擬整個地球。<br />\nMicrosoft Azure技術生成了世界要素（例如地形，樹木，草叢，建築物和水）的3D表示。<br />\n通過使用Azure Cloud來呈現視覺效果，模擬現實世界的數據和效果。<br />\n<br />\n大家都一齊係到討論下,無論玩開咩平台都可以一齊討論,一齊推post,亦歡迎傾下航空界消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIVAO East Asia Region (又被戲稱為大東亞共榮圈): <a href=\"https://xe.ivao.aero/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxe.ivao.aero%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=b0fca49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xe.ivao.aero/</a><br />\nIVAO水塘FB group: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ivaohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fivaohk%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=9ac0cb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/ivaohk/</a><br />\nFlight Simulator 模擬飛行 Fans Club: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/208288605877832/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F208288605877832%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=4a0f4161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/208288605877832/</a><br />\n香港模擬飛行社群 Flight Sim Community Hong Kong: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/580179355476956/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F580179355476956%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=27e22786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/580179355476956/</a><br />\nFlight Simulator Hong Kong 香港模擬飛行及航空管制: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/flightsimhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fflightsimhk&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=fe2d97a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/flightsimhk</a><br />\n<br />\n香港東行航路M750/A1小貼士: <a href=\"https://xe.ivao.aero/a1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxe.ivao.aero%2Fa1%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ab282ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xe.ivao.aero/a1/</a><br />\n香港虛擬航空公司列表:<br />\nAir Golden: <a href=\"http://goldenair.co.uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoldenair.co.uk%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=1bcdc790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goldenair.co.uk/</a><br />\nOasis Hong Kong Virtual: <a href=\"http://voasis.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvoasis.org%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=839ac06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://voasis.org/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手專區:<br />\n<br />\nQ1: 玩開FSX，咩係P3D?咩係MSFS?<br />\nA1: FSX係Microsoft開發嘅Flight Simulator其中一個版本，「最新」版本係FSX SP2，已經係2006年嘅產品。<br />\n而P3D就係由Lockheed Martin向Microsoft買斷咗FSX商用版(ESP)嘅版權再開發而成嘅，主要改善咗DirectX嘅支援，修正咗啲FSX會crash嘅bugs，仲有更好嘅記憶體使用。<br />\nDovetail曾經喺Microsoft手上買斷家用版FSX嘅版權，喺FSX SP2上面改善咗喺Steam上面Multiplayer嘅功能。後來Microsoft回購，再加以改良，成為MSFS。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 電腦要咩spec先玩得順？<br />\nA2: P3D: <a href=\"http://www.prepar3d.com/system-requirements/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prepar3d.com%2Fsystem-requirements%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=0eb8de44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.prepar3d.com/system-requirements/</a><br />\nX-Plane 11: <a href=\"http://www.x-plane.com/kb/x-plane-11-system-requirements/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.x-plane.com%2Fkb%2Fx-plane-11-system-requirements%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=2d59825d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.x-plane.com/kb/x-plane-11-system-requirements/</a><br />\nMSFS: <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1250410/Microsoft_Flight_Simulator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1250410%2FMicrosoft_Flight_Simulator%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=a67b12ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1250410/Microsoft_Flight_Simulator/</a><br />\nSimulation好講即時反應，所以佢啲畫面冇得大量pre-render出黎，所以對CPU嘅要求就比較高。揀CPU最好就係揀粒單核時脈高嘅CPU，例如係Intel i7-10700K可以OC到5.1GHz。<br />\n同市面上大部份遊戲一樣，多核心支援較差，所以唔使揀多核心但低時脈嘅CPU。<br />\n至於GPU，主要唔係用黎影像渲染(frame rendering)，而係處理抗鋸齒(Anti Aliasing, AA)，唔需要用太高階。但多數都推薦NVIDIA，可配合NVIDIA inspector改settings。<br />\n<br />\n搖桿悉隨尊便<br />\n新手推薦用Xbox controller試吓先<br />\n因為你第時唔玩flightsim都最少可以玩其他game<br />\n之後就Logitech Extreme 3D Pro<br />\n之後Thrustmaster睇價錢揀<br />\nYoke就honeycomb成套<br />\nRudder就Thrustmaster TPR pedal<br />\n<br />\nQ3:咩係addon？點先可以有靚機場？<br />\nA3:其實addon即係好常見嘅DLC咁，追加遊戲內容，玩得更多更真實。<br />\nFSX/P3D你當佢只係提供個地球同埋aerodynamic嘅基本，所以好多時都需要買addon返黎增加flight sim嘅樂趣。<br />\n但同addon好少由官方自己出。多數都係由3rd party開發嘅addon<br />\n以下係一啲addon廠推介： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/O1mNqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FO1mNqc&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=7d2b8bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/O1mNqc</a><br />\n<br />\nQ5: 咩係P3D v4/v5？做乜咁期待？<br />\nA5: P3D依家出到version 5，期待係因為LM喺v4中轉咗用64bit code去寫依個Application，<br />\n徹底解決Q4中提到最常彈game嘅原因（32bit&rarr;用完4GB VAS&rarr;OOM)。<br />\n<br />\nQ6: 喺邊度有Crack？<br />\nA6: 請支持正版。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ7: 英文洗唔洗好勁?ATC點講?<br />\nA7: 唔洗，有1套簡單既ATC radio用語要記，keep it simple and clear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://xe.ivao.aero/pilot/vhhh/#tab-ifr-example\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxe.ivao.aero%2Fpilot%2Fvhhh%2F%23tab-ifr-example&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=5b78a05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xe.ivao.aero/pilot/vhhh/#tab-ifr-example</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6321b42b26668556fd0d0b344d81abfc8e935fa0","tid":2455120,"uid":236866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T00:12:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4fb81acd1baa79a2efd027c1b48dc144bcc8896f","tid":2455120,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"45f5cc7cd6fc3b65fed69376e5dde90b631c989a","tid":2455120,"uid":110036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b072a2dda25417c8e38847aba972a397b0e246","tid":2455120,"uid":77408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f5cc7cd6fc3b65fed69376e5dde90b631c989a","tid":2455120,"uid":110036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8edc300ff6522231c8b3a5df552a6598fc6d43","tid":2455120,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b072a2dda25417c8e38847aba972a397b0e246","tid":2455120,"uid":77408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f5cc7cd6fc3b65fed69376e5dde90b631c989a","tid":2455120,"uid":110036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"話唔定過一排會返生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}